{"id":100922,"date":"2014-12-16T17:46:26","date_gmt":"2014-12-16T16:46:26","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.www.convergences.org\/?p=100922"},"modified":"2016-07-21T15:23:25","modified_gmt":"2016-07-21T13:23:25","slug":"save-the-date-11th-microcredit-week","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.convergences.org\/en\/save-the-date-11th-microcredit-week\/","title":{"rendered":"SAVE THE DATE : 11th microcredit week"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>From february 2 to 6, Adie will hold the 11th microcredit week<br \/>\n<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-100912\" src=\"https:\/\/www.convergences.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/adie.jpg\" alt=\"adie\" width=\"315\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.convergences.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/adie.jpg 315w, https:\/\/www.convergences.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/adie-236x300.jpg 236w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 315px) 100vw, 315px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><strong>&#8221; <em>And you, what do you do for employment ?&#8221;<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p>For the international year of microcredit initatied by the UN in 2005, Adie organized the first microcredit week.<\/p>\n<p>Adie is currently creating more than 200 jobs per week. During the microcredit week, participants are able to <strong>create their own micro-entreprise<\/strong> thanks to a supportive microcredit scheme. Participants will also be able to take part in information meetings which will be held in the headquarters of these newly-established enterprises.<\/p>\n<p>During the 2014 Convergences World Forum, Adie was nominated for the European Convergences Awards. If you would like to learn more about their project in partnership with AXA and MACIF, feel free to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.convergences.org\/bibliotheque\/booklet-des-prix-convergences-2014\/\">click here.<\/a><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">